{"title":"我伴小平上白山","authors":["晓初"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":2,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高路远多盘旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下车健步登高望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林海葱茏喜壮观。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天高云淡丹阳暄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一泓琼液引人醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两袖清风擎九天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林阴深处有温泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖瀑布如珠串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎啸龙吟震泥潭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天池映日尽开颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美人松下黄莺叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万木丛中鸣杜鹃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东西岭外有平原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三江注满天池水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸农家灌稻田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未忘昔日起烽烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗联将士多忠烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日寇汉奸心胆寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伴小平上白山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑谈包产又丰年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三中全会好方策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万工农展笑颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者曾任吉林省委书记，一九八三年夏初，曾陪同邓小平同志登长白山。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}